graph LR
    ODH["odh-model-controller<br/>+ model-serving-api"]

    %% Required External Dependencies
    ODH -->|CRD Watch<br/>InferenceService, ServingRuntime,<br/>InferenceGraph, LLMInferenceService| KServe["KServe<br/>v0.17.0-rc1<br/>(ODH fork)"]
    ODH -->|framework| CR["controller-runtime<br/>v0.19.7"]
    ODH -->|ServiceMonitor,<br/>PodMonitor| PromOp["Prometheus Operator<br/>v0.89.0"]
    ODH -->|webhook TLS certs| CertManager["cert-manager<br/>v1.16.3"]
    ODH -->|Route, Template,<br/>Authentication APIs| OpenShift["OpenShift API<br/>v0.0.0-20260306"]

    %% Optional External Dependencies
    ODH -.->|AuthPolicy for<br/>Gateway + HTTPRoute| Kuadrant["Kuadrant<br/>v1.4.2"]
    ODH -.->|auth provider<br/>TLS config watch| Authorino["Authorino<br/>v0.22.0"]
    ODH -.->|EnvoyFilter<br/>TLS bootstrap| Istio["Istio client-go<br/>v1.27.8"]
    ODH -.->|TriggerAuth<br/>Prometheus autoscaling| KEDA["KEDA<br/>v2.18.3"]
    ODH -.->|Gateway, HTTPRoute<br/>for LLM ingress| GatewayAPI["Gateway API<br/>v1.2.1"]
    ODH -.->|InferencePool<br/>advanced routing| GatewayInf["Gateway API<br/>Inference Ext<br/>v1.3.1"]
    ODH -.->|Model Registry<br/>InferenceService reg| KFHub["Kubeflow Hub<br/>v0.3.9"]

    %% Internal Platform Dependencies
    ODH -->|CRD Read:<br/>DSC, DSCI| RHOAIOp["rhods-operator /<br/>opendatahub-operator"]
    ODH -->|metrics scrape config| Prometheus["OpenShift<br/>Monitoring"]

    %% Integration Points (consumers)
    Dashboard["RHOAI Dashboard"] -->|GET /api/v1/gateways<br/>HTTPS/8443| ODH
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| ODH

    %% External Services
    ODH -->|API key validation<br/>model catalog| NGC["NVIDIA NGC API<br/>api.ngc.nvidia.com"]
    ODH -->|registry auth<br/>pull secrets| NVCR["NVIDIA NVCR<br/>nvcr.io"]
    ODH -->|all CRUD ops| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>Server"]

